snippet.title: Cubians: Rescue Princess - Trailer [VR, HTC Vive]
snippet.description:
Trailer for Cubians: Rescue Princess, a voxel-style virtual reality rhythm puzzle game where players need to rescue the princess by exploring a fairy tale world. Developed by IKINA GAMES, available for HTC Vive. You can find more information, as well as reviews and ratings here: https://vrgamecritic.com/game/cubians-rescue-princess
